      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>This small device is often worn strapped to the back of the neck or attached to a helmet. When activated, an emotion regulator sends out regular neurological pulses, reigning in extreme emotions.</p>\n<p>An advanced emotion regulator is more effective at suppressing a broader range of extreme emotions, granting you a +2 insight bonus to saves against emotion, fear, mind-affecting, and pain effects. In addition, you are undetectable to blindsense (emotion) and blindsight (emotion). An advanced emotion regulator does not impart penalties.</p>\n<p><strong>Capacity&nbsp;</strong> 100; <strong>Usage&nbsp;</strong> 1/10 minutes</p>"
